This documentation describes the Dynatrace Full-Stack Add-on for Pivotal Platform. The Dynatrace Full-Stack Add-on
for Pivotal Platform enables operators to roll out Dynatrace OneAgent to both Pivotal Application Service (PAS) and Pivotal Container Service (PKS) clusters and installed tiles for monitoring the platform and deployed apps.


## <a id='overview'></a> Overview

Dynatrace Full-Stack Add-on for Pivotal Platform enables monitoring of Pivotal Platform components like Pivotal Elastic Runtime/Pivotal Application Service (PAS), Pivotal Application Service for Windows/Pivotal Platform Runtime for Windows, Pivotal Container Service (PKS), and all applications deployed to Pivotal Platform (PAS and/or PKS). After the Dynatrace Full-Stack Add-on for Pivotal Platform is deployed to the platform, Dynatrace OneAgent automatically begins monitoring any deployed apps. Developers can use the Dynatrace web UI to get insights into the performance of their apps and microservices.


## <a id='features'></a> Key Features

Dynatrace Full-Stack Add-on includes the following key features:

* Monitoring of Pivotal Platform components
* Automatic monitoring of deployed apps across both PAS and PKS
* Automatic distributed tracing of microservices across both PAS and PKS
* Automatic discovery of deployment dependencies and communication behavior
* Automatic root-cause analysis and AI-based problem detection


